TEXT(&beginproblem);
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,20,1);
$b = random(2,20,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Suppose that \( f(x) = (x+$a)^{$b} \ln(x) \).  Find \(f'(1)\).

$BR $BR

\(f'(1)\) = \{ans_rule(30) \}
$BR

EOT

$ans = (1+$a)**($b);
